{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act14side_level_act14side_02_beg","storyGroup":"act14side","storySort":4,"storyDependence":"act14side_level_act14side_st01","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BI-2","storyName":"息事宁人","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"神秘女子雅儿与博士展开了交谈，恩希亚决心去找博士。\nSharp与极光正要为营救博士而行动，雅儿带来了博士的指令。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act14side/level_act14side_02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act14side_02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":2,"next":4,"characters":["邻居","极光","极光的姐姐","Sharp","耶拉","恩希亚","雅儿","角峰"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_bg_24_g9_manoravenue.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"洛拉，一回家就帮忙干活，真孝顺啊。","id":10,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"哪里，是我应该做的，我也想到处走走。","id":12,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"哎，出去学习过的就是不一样，比我弟弟懂事多了。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"多好的一个姑娘，真可惜。","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"搬家之后，不知道还找不找得到你这么好的姑娘了。","id":18,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"欸，莎莎姐，你不是在这里住得好好的吗，怎么要搬家啦？","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"还不是我爸。昨天不是三族议会上宣布要让圣女来管三大家吗？","id":22,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"我爸这不就来劲了。","id":24,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"啊......佐尔叔一直都反对恩希欧迪斯老爷的开放政策呢......","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"可不是嘛，当年我们一家是为了我弟和我的工作从北边搬过来。","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"本来呢，这些年磨着磨着，我爸也差不多习惯了。","id":30,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"结果昨天还政这事一宣布，他可高兴了。","id":32,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"昨晚吃饭的时候就一直在骂恩希欧迪斯老爷这些年做的事，我都听烦了，还跟他吵了一架。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"但也拗不过老头子，说不定我们家就要搬回佩尔罗契家的领地去了。","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"那你弟弟的工作呢？","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"谁知道呢，这次还政完，不知道图里卡姆能不能还像以前那样做生意呢。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"我听佩尔罗契那边的说法啊，本来上次三族议会上也是圣女大人要恩希欧迪斯老爷交出谷地和矿区呢。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"要是圣女大人来管谢拉格，恩希欧迪斯老爷估计讨不了好吧。","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#3$1","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"......也是。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8f/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"不过，这也是好事。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"你这几年在外面可能不知道，一开始三大家族之间还挺配合的，但是最近啊，他们互相是越来越不对付。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"上次议会之后很多人都觉得怕是要打起来了。","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"......是呢，没想到这次恩希欧迪斯老爷居然让步了，而且是让圣女大人来掌权。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"对啊，不过要我说，早该这么办了，虽然我不讨厌恩希欧迪斯老爷的开放政策，毕竟我们家也跟着赚了不少钱。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"但是，有的时候也确实觉得和老人们说的一样，谢拉格变得不再像谢拉格了。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"现在恩希欧迪斯老爷决定让步，事情别闹太大，大家都是赞成的。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_280_1#1$1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"邻居","text":"大概也就你哥那种老顽固反对了。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_280_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"我哥......","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":65},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":66},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":67},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":68},{"type":"character","id":69},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_bg_24_g5_guestroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":70},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":71},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#9$1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"我回来了。","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2e/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_276_1#1$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光的姐姐","text":"唉，傻孩子，说了让你回来就好好休息，非要干活。","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_276_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光的姐姐","text":"（轻声）你这个什么石什么病的，你不心疼自己的身体状况，我们还心疼得紧呢。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_276_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#9$1","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"没事，姐，这点活还不碍事。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2e/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"咦，哥哥呢？","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_276_1#1$1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光的姐姐","text":"他说要去一趟工厂，刚才急匆匆地出门了，还说今天不会回来了。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/07/Avg_avg_npc_276_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"工厂？","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.6","id":87},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":88},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":89},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"是队长？","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":92},{"type":"character","id":93},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"1","id":95},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":96,"musicid":1},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","name":"avg_npc_252","style":"cutin","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"-300","width":"200","block":"true","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"队长，有什么事吗？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"假期结束了，极光。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_char_empty.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"-1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"博士昨天在车站被佩尔罗契家的人接走了。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_char_empty.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"哎？！","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"博士是自愿和他们走的，你应该明白我的意思，他多半有什么计划了。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_char_empty.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我大致看了一下地图，从车站到佩尔罗契家要一段时间。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_char_empty.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"现在，博士现在应该已经到佩尔罗契家了，我们也该行动了。","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_char_empty.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我现在借口去你家看看状况，然后出来和你会合。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_char_empty.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"好的。","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":116},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"1","id":117},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":119},{"type":"character","name":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"......先去和队长会合吧。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":122},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":125},{"type":"character","id":126},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":127},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":129},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"原来如此，你就是那个罗德岛的人啊。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":133},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":134},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"136","text":"原来你不认识我。"},"2":{"id":"136","text":"你并不是特意找上我的。"}},"values":[],"id":135},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":136,"end":140},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"是啊。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"你很独特，但我也不知道你为什么很独特。","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":141},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":142},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"144","text":"你在市场说的，是什么意思？"}},"values":[],"id":143},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":144,"end":150},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"嗯？","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"一点忠告而已。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"你看，结果不是得被一群陌生人盯着，连出门逛逛都不自在吗？","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":151},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":152},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"154","text":"你知道些什么？"}},"values":[],"id":153},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":154,"end":156},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"在回答你这个问题之前，先告诉我，你来谢拉格是为了什么？","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":158},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"160","text":"出于和喀兰贸易的商业合作。"},"2":"帮崖心修复兄妹关系。","3":"旅游。"},"values":["2","3"],"id":159},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":160,"end":162},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"也就是说，你是恩希欧迪斯的朋友？","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":164},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"166","text":"视情况而定。"}},"values":[],"id":165},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":166,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["2"],"id":167},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"修复希瓦艾什家三兄妹的关系？","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"你的口气很大哦。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":172},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"那你可倒霉了，莫名其妙就被卷进了这样的事。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"不过我可不相信，一个在这种环境下还能优哉游哉的人，是真的打着旅游的主意来的。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":177},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"我很好奇——像你这样的外来者，是如何看待谢拉格这个地方的。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":180},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":181},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"183","text":"这里很安宁。"},"2":{"id":"192","text":"信仰很虔诚。"},"3":{"id":"205","text":"落后。"}},"values":[],"id":182},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":183,"end":191},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"安宁......是啊，这里已经安宁了一千多年了。","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"安宁也意味着停滞。","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"谢拉格的人们太过习惯于这种状态，以至于他们不在乎外面在发生什么，也不感兴趣。","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"这应该是一件好事，但最近，我又觉得......唉......","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":192,"end":204},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"毕竟对耶拉冈德的信仰是将这片土地上的人们凝聚在一起的根本。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"但是，有的时候，我也会觉得，人们有些太过依赖信仰。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"你能明白吗？你将你的烦恼向神倾诉，期待着神来帮你解决，然后就会变成——","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"明明该用自己的意志去改变境况，却只把神意当作停滞的借口。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"明明是用自己的双手去耕耘得来的收获，却要在事后感激神明的慷慨。","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"明明真正做出了选择，付出了努力的，应该是每个人自己......","id":204,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":205,"end":219},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"真直接。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"不过，像你这样来自外面......按新说法，“外国”的人，大多都抱着这样的看法。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"外面的人们早已发展出了许多能够让人偷懒，或者说，省力的技术。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"他们对便利的生活习以为常，而大多谢拉格人还不曾接触过这些。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"或许生活在谢拉格的人们确实能在这不够便利的生活中锤炼出勤劳和勇敢，能从远离享乐的环境里学习到信仰和美德。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"但我也不觉得这是应当永恒持续的事情。","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"谢拉格人开拓了这片雪山之间的乐土，但他们是否能够只靠传统来维持家园的坚实稳固？","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"在你看来，谢拉格应该做出改变吗？","id":222,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":223},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":224},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"226","text":"需要。"},"2":{"id":"233","text":"不能一概而论。"},"3":{"id":"240","text":"我还不够了解这里。"}},"values":[],"id":225},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":226,"end":232},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"哎，你也这么想吗。","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"其实明眼人都看得出来，恩希欧迪斯带来的变革是无法停止的。","id":230,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"谁又能轻易拒绝让自己的生活变得更轻松、更方便一些呢。","id":232,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":233,"end":239},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"我还以为你会说，这一切落后的事物都应该被改变。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"我已经听许多人说过这样的话了。","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"而这些人，大多反而是土生土长的谢拉格人。","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":240,"end":246},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"真谨慎。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"不过，我并不讨厌谨慎的人。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"只可惜，你可能已经没有多少时间去了解这个国家现在的样貌了。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":247},{"type":"dialog","id":248},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":249},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"251","text":"所以，你知道些什么？"}},"values":[],"id":250},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":251,"end":267},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"我......","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"我有一个朋友。","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"我的这个朋友，一直在思考，怎么样才能让谢拉格变得更好。","id":257,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"但是，她想了很久，也想不出一个结果。","id":259,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"她逐渐发现，每个人想的都和她不一样，而这些人的想法，无论哪一个，都令她感到不安。","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"她想要做些什么，但是每当她想要做些什么时，总有人劝阻她。","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"而且，她发现，她已经逐渐无法阻止那些人想要做的事了。","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"就在这时，你来了。","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":268},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":269},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"271","text":"你认为这是一种预兆？"}},"values":[],"id":270},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":271,"end":277},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"预兆？或许用病急乱投医来解释更合适。","id":273,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"一个接受恩希欧迪斯的邀请，来自异国他乡的人，你的光谱和气息让我感到异样的陌生与新奇——","id":275,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耶拉","text":"告诉我，外乡人，你的到来，意味着什么？","id":277,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_251.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":278},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_251","focus":"-1","id":279},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"281","text":"......"}},"values":[],"id":280},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":281},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"283","text":"说起来，你可以先帮我一个忙。"}},"values":[],"id":282},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":283,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":285},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":287},{"type":"character","id":288},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/88/Avg_bg_24_g8_nobleroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":290},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":291,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":293},{"type":"subtitle","text":"展信佳。\\n恩希亚，听说你回到了谢拉格，姐姐很开心。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":294},{"type":"subtitle","text":"虽然姐姐不能下山来见你，但听到你健康安全的消息，姐姐心里就比什么都要高兴。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":295},{"type":"subtitle","text":"听说这一次，帮你治疗矿石病的人也随你一起来了谢拉格，有机会的话，姐姐真想当面向他们道谢。\\n他们拯救了我的妹妹，理应获得来自耶拉冈德的祝福。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":296},{"type":"subtitle","text":"要记得去向其他家的人问好，报告你平安的消息，早睡早起，也不要忘了每天两次向耶拉冈德的祷告，还有，不准爬山......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":297},{"type":"subtitle","text":"好吧，我想，你一定嫌姐姐啰嗦了，姐姐就不唠叨了。\\n祝你这一次回家玩得开心，恩希亚。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":298},{"type":"subtitle","text":"姐姐会在耶拉冈德面前为你祈福的。\\n另：要是你也能给姐姐写回信就更好了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":299},{"type":"subtitle","id":300},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":301},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"明明上次收到姐姐的信后也没过多久，姐姐真是，好像很久没有写信了一样，每次都这么唠叨。","id":303,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e3/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"谢谢你，雅儿姐，每次都帮我把姐姐的信送过来。","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/28/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"没事，圣女大人不能随意下山，我替她在外面走一走，给她带去外面的消息，这也是她的心愿。","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"不过抱歉，我暂时没有办法给姐姐回信，我现在要准备别的事情。","id":309,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/12/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"看你旁边的包......你打算出门？","id":311,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"是的。","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0d/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"你要去哪儿？去攀登少女峰吗？","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"哎呀，你不说我都忘了，我至今还没有征服少女峰呢！","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"不过我这次要去的，是谷地。","id":319,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/28/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#3$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"谷地？那里不是正要移交给蔓珠院吗，而且那里好多工厂，你要去干什么？","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#3$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"因为博士会去那里，我要去见见博士。啊，雅儿姐，你还不知道博士是谁吧？","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/28/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"啊，我听说了，是那个被佩尔罗契家带走的客人吗？","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"嗯。博士毕竟是我的客人，不看到博士平安我心里过意不去。","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0d/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"真是个好孩子。","id":329,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#6$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"不过你当心些，我听说那边最近不太平。","id":331,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5f/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#6$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"嗯。","id":333,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/28/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_199_yak_1#1$1","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"角峰","text":"二小姐，可以出发了。","id":335,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/71/Avg_avg_199_yak_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_199_yak_1#1$1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"角峰","text":"不必担心，这次出行，所有的责任由我承担。","id":337,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/71/Avg_avg_199_yak_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"角峰叔，给你添麻烦了。","id":339,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0d/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_199_yak_1#8$1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"角峰","text":"二小姐难得认真请我帮忙，我怎么会有不帮的道理。","id":341,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/35/Avg_avg_199_yak_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"恩希亚","text":"雅儿姐，我可能要出去比较久，请回去告诉姐姐，我之后再给她回信吧。","id":343,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/28/Avg_avgnew_173_slchan_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","name2":"avgnew_173_slchan_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"没事没事，我可以等的。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":346},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":347},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":348},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":349},{"type":"character","id":350},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_bg_24_g1_snowyforest.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":351},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":352},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$escape_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_escape_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":353,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":355},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":356},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"极光，我需要信息来做判断，尤其是来自你这个本地人的观点，说说你对博士处境的看法。","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"诺希斯作为矿区和谷地的前负责人，所处的位置应当十分敏感。","id":361,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"眼下恩希欧迪斯老爷将博士放在了这个人的位置上，势必会引起阿克托斯的关注。","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"详细说说矿区和谷地的敏感原因。","id":365,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"嗯......要是手边有地图的话会方便一些。","id":367,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_24_i01.png","fadetime":"2","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","id":368},{"type":"imagetween","image":"24_i01","tiled":"true","xScaleTo":"1.0","yScaleTo":"1.0","duration":"25","block":"false","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"谢拉格的地形不算很复杂，也没有很细致的划分。","id":370,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"一般，我们本地人一般都是直接叫矿区、谷地、林地、湖区、山区、溪地、平原的。","id":371,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"溪地和平原，以及大半的湖区是北边的佩尔罗契家的。","id":372,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"西边的布朗陶家领地以林地为主，以及小部分湖区。","id":373,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"希瓦艾什家则主要是山区、谷地和矿区，湖区的部分几乎可以忽略不计。","id":374,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"而谷地和矿区......其实已经能够代表将近一半的希瓦艾什家的领地。","id":375,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"其中，矿区一直以来都是希瓦艾什家非常重要的领地，因为整个谢拉格用的矿石几乎都是这里产出的。","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"而谷地则是近年发展起来的。","id":377,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"原本，谷地是一块非常贫瘠的土地，连村庄也没有几个，一直被认为是一块没有用的土地。","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"但是，恩希欧迪斯老爷建立喀兰贸易后，就将这片区域选作了工厂用地。","id":379,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"喀兰贸易的大部分制造工厂都建造在那里，而且这一部分很靠近喀兰圣山。","id":380,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":381},{"type":"character","id":382},{"type":"image","fadetime":"1","id":383},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":384},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"此外，出发前我和一些谢拉格商人交换过信息——不过出来做生意的人也都和喀兰贸易有关。","id":386,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"一个月前，在圣女大人的支持下，布朗陶家和佩尔罗契家要求并组织了一支调查工厂安全隐患问题的队伍。","id":388,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"但是这支队伍却遭到了拒不配合的诺希斯暗中指使的袭击。我不知道消息是怎么传出来的，但所有人都相信此事与诺希斯有关。","id":390,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"这导致了佩尔罗契家的家主阿克托斯在蔓珠院的授意下派兵进驻了谷地，而诺希斯也是因此次过激行动造成的后果才被革职。","id":392,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"会议上，博士提到过，恩希欧迪斯邀请他的理由。","id":394,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"虽然确实有协助喀兰贸易进行矿石病相关设施的建设，但完全没提过要让博士替他管理任何事务。","id":395,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"也就是说，博士已经主动踏到阴谋的天平之上了，很像是他会做的事情。","id":397,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"这种可能性很高，但是，喀兰贸易与罗德岛的关系并不差，博士应当也是因为有这层关系才会接受邀请。","id":399,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"我暂时想不到恩希欧迪斯老爷要陷害博士的理由......","id":401,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":402},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"现在怎么办？联络凯尔希医生？","id":403,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"本舰正在前往维多利亚，除非使用本地的大型通讯基站，否则只靠我们携带的设备是没办法联络本舰的。","id":405,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"（长叹一口气）","id":407,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"队长......？","id":409,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我观察了一段时间，博士目前的驻留地防备力量并不强。","id":411,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"佩尔罗契家的宅邸大概有卫兵两百人，训练和武器都不及外界正规军，靠突然袭击可以突破。","id":412,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"周围的地形我也做过确认，另一个方案是渗透进入，不过这需要在多处提前做好爆破准备。","id":414,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"在进入和撤离时都需要制造爆炸来吸引注意力，有几处墙面结构可以......","id":415,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"等一下！队长！","id":417,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/28/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"嗯？","id":419,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"我觉得......事情还不会发展到那一步才对。","id":421,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"无论发生什么事，都要保证博士的安全，这是我的第一要务。","id":423,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"......这个我同意，但是......","id":425,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"临近大典，我们在佩尔罗契家族的领地动武，那罗德岛恐怕会成为喀兰圣山之敌。","id":427,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"罗德岛上的那些谢拉格干员怎么办？","id":429,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我需要随时考虑最坏的可能性，以及最不体面的解决方法。眼下的事态不乐观，如果我一定要做出选择，你知道我只会选择博士。","id":431,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我们都希望事情不要发展到这一步，但你也知道，这不取决于我们，我要对博士和罗德岛负责。","id":433,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"我总觉得......恩希欧迪斯老爷可能有自己的想法。","id":435,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"既然选择了将计就计，想必博士早就察觉到了端倪，而且已经准备好应对手段了吧......","id":437,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我从来都不会质疑博士的能力，我相信他。","id":439,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"但是我需要提前做好准备，博士让我待命，那他的计划里就有我们的位置。","id":441,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":442},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"我们得先和博士联络一下。","id":443,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"极光。","id":445,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"嗯？","id":447,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"你很尊敬恩希欧迪斯。","id":449,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"......是的。没有恩希欧迪斯老爷，我是不可能走出谢拉格，接触外面的一切的。","id":451,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2e/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我可以理解。","id":453,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"但我要你暂时忘了这件事，现在开始，你要将他视为假想敌，能不能做到？","id":455,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"如果觉得做不到，你现在可以回去，我不会责怪你。","id":457,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"......但我同时也是罗德岛的一员。","id":459,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"记住你现在说的话。","id":461,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"是。","id":463,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"极光","text":"但是......我们也要提防崖心他们吗？","id":465,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_422_aurora_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"我相信崖心，但我不信任恩希亚·希瓦艾什。","id":467,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_422_aurora_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"接下来就是想想要怎么去见博士。","id":469,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":470},{"type":"character","id":471},{"type":"delay","time":"1.2","id":472},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowbootwalk","id":473},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":474},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"你们就是博士的部下吧？","id":476,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","id":477},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":478},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":479},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":480},{"type":"playsound","key":"$knifegore","volume":"1","id":481},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"......（斩击）","id":483,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":484},{"type":"character","id":485},{"type":"text","text":"一瞬间，坚钢的长刀划过了空气，停在了少女颈部的毫厘之外。","id":486},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"哇，这个刀法，很少见哦。","id":488,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"......什么人？","id":490,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":491},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"那个，没有必要对刚见面的普通少女这么凶恶吧。","id":492,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":493},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Sharp","text":"能定位到这里，还能在这种局面下开玩笑的，算普通少女吗？","id":494,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_252.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":495},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"先把刀放下啦！是罗德岛的博士让我来找你们的。","id":496,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_252","name2":"avg_npc_250_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"雅儿","text":"博士有话让我带给你们。","id":498,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_250_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":499},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":500},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":501},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":502},{"type":"character","id":503},{"type":"image","id":504}],"characters":["邻居","极光","极光的姐姐","Sharp","耶拉","恩希亚","雅儿","角峰"]}